txt.en: 'The voice shall rule all of Moria.'
'The voice will find you, and then you will die.'
'You shall fall to the voice. Moria belongs to him now.'
'Moria belongs to the goblins, not the longbeards!'
'We stare down at you at all hours, waiting for my mighty hand to signal their attack.'
'Know this, soil-worm: the goblins will always rule these halls!'
